item.title: -AlienScape- NEW SERVER TEAM!
item.dc:creator: @lothy Lothy
item.description:
@lothy wrote:

No offence, but real teams don’t have a monarch type system where there is an “owner” and the like. I don’t see why people should have to be better then you to work under you.
Personally, I’m not joining. I’m already part of a 3 person team building a kick ass server, and it’s a team where everybody has equal rights and say. Not one where there are ranks.
Ranks in a community are fine, but ranks in a small team with a common goal aren’t.

Read full topic
